snippet.textDisplay:
Noor vo hota hae jo andheree surang kae dosray seray par nazar aa'ta hae, goya kisi pahari say girta pheglay sonay ka chashma ho.

Insaan kya karay kae asmano aur zameen jitna Noor mil jaye? Vo Allah ko NA kehna chour dae, phir osay otna Noor melay ga kae us ki sari dunya Roshan hojayege.

Aur kaesay milta hae Noor? Jo Allah ki Jitni maanta hae osay otna he Noor milta hae. Kisi ka Noor pahaar jitna, kisi ka darakht jitna, kisi ka shoulay jitna, aur kisi ka paao kae anghotay jitna. Anghotay jitna Noor?, jo jalta bujhta hae, Bujhta Jalta, yeh on logo ko deya jata hae jo kuch din bauhat dil laga kar bauhat Naik amal kartay hae aur phir sab chour chaar kar Depression mae ghar baeth jatay hae.

Allah Noor hae, Asmaan aur Zameen ka, aur suno, dil ko maray bagaer Noor nahe mela karta!

snippet.textDisplay:
The covers or remakes I loved from this season:

Episode 1:
Ali Sethi - Ranjish Hi Sahi

Episode 2:
Junoon Ft RFAK, Ali Noor - Sayonee
Kaavish, Quratulain Balouch - Faasle
Ali Zafar - Jaan-e-Bahaaraan 

Episode 3:
Sahir Ali Bagga, Aima Baig - Baazi

Episode 4:
Javed Bashir, Akbar Ali Ft Aamir Zaki - Naina Moray

Episode 5:
Attaullah Esakhelvi, Sanwal Esakhelvi - Sab Maya Hai
RFAK - Rangrez

Episode 6:
Umair Jaswal, Jabar Abbas - Dam Mast Qalandar (This one is less favourite as compared to other ones, just felt that this type of vocal style has been covered so many times, it could've been differently amazing)

Episode 7: 
Sajjad Ali - Tera Naam (Don't know but it does sound like the old Pakistani song Tera Naam Hatheli' to me. However a beautiful song).
Shuja Haider, Aima Baig - Baanware (Mostly because of Shuja Haider's voice chords)
